## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent bias in sources that may have political leanings. Additionally, the complexity of measuring corruption means that indices like Transparency International's may not capture all nuances of the issue. Further research could benefit from more recent data and a broader range of perspectives.